p: In the District Court holding terms at Seattle, in King County, Washington Territory
In the matter of the Application of Ah Fong for a Writ of Habeas Corpus} No. Applications for writ of Habeas Corpus
To the Honorable Roger S. Greene Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of Washington Territory and Judge of the above entitled Court.
The petition of Ah Fong respectfully shows

That said Ah Fong is unlawfully imprisoned, detained, confined and restrained of his liberty by William Murphy Acting Chief Police of said City of Seattle in the City Jail at Seattle in King County, Washington Territory that the said Ah Fong is a subject of the Emperor of China

That the cause or pretense of said restraint according to the best knowledge and belief of this applicant is this, to wit: that said Ah Fong was accused of violating a certain pretended
